quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,46,"Waxaanu ahayn kuwa beeniya Maalinta abaal marinta (jaazeynta)."
  74,47,"Jeer ay noo timid yaqiinta la hubo (geeridu)."
  74,48,"Marka waxba u tarimeyso shafeecada kuwa shafeeca."
  77,34,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  77,35,"Kanu waa Maalin aysan (gaaladu) hadleyn."
  77,36,"Oo aan idan la siineyn si ay u cudurdaartaan."
  78,31,"Kuwa Alle ka cabsada ee (ka) dhowrsada (xumaha) waxay leeyihiin meel lagu liibaano (Janno)."
  78,32,"Beero iyo canabyo."
  78,33,"Iyo gashaantiyo da' yar oo isla eg."
  79,25,"Markaasuu Alle ku dhigay ciqaab lagu tusaale qaato (xadgudubkii) dambe (sheegashadiisa ilaahnimo) iyo tii hore darteed (beeninta Muuse)."
  79,26,"Arrinkani waxaa ugu sugan cibrad (digniin) qof kastoo ka baqa Alle."
  79,27,"Ma idinkaa adag abuur ahaan, mise samada, wuu dhisay."
  80,22,"Markuu doonana wuu soo bixin."
  80,23,"Mayee, ma uusan yeelin wuxuu amray."
  80,24,"Ee qofku bal ha eego cunnadiisa."
  81,19,"Hubaal kani (Qur'aanka) waa hadal (Ilaahay) uu keenay Rasuul sharaf badan (Jabriil)."
  81,20,"Awood iyo meeqaan sare ku leh (Alle) agtiis, Rabbiga Carshiga Weyn,"
  81,21,"La adeeco, haddana aamin ah kalsooni lagu qabo."
  82,13,"Baarriyadu waxay dhex ahaan barwaaqo (Janno)."
  82,14,"Xume falayaashuna waxay ku sugnaan Naar ololaysa."
  82,15,"Ay geli oo ku guban Maalinta Is abaalmarinta (Jaazeynta)."
  83,10,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  83,11,"Kuwa beeniya Maalinta is abaal marinta (Qiyaamada)."
  83,12,"Cidina ma beeniso aan aheyn xadgudbe kastoo denbiile ah."
  84,7,"Ee ma kan lagu siiyo Kitaabkiisa gacantiisa midig,"
  84,8,"Waxaa la xisaabin xisaab fudud."
  84,9,"Wuxuu u laaban ehelkiisa (Jannada ku sugan) isagoo faraxsan."
  85,4,"Lacnadi ha ku dhacdo qoladii godka lahaa (mu'miniinta lagu caddibo)."
  85,5,"Ee ahaa dab olol iyo huritaan badan."
  85,6,"Iyagoo (gaaladu) kor fadhiyeen (godka)."